description: EXCLUSIVE BY MATT BARLOW: 'I could've stayed on,' Rimmer remembers. 'We'd worked hard to get there and we wanted to win. I cried in the dressing room.'
title: Jimmy Rimmer believed the 1982 European Cup final would be his finest hour, but unknown Nigel Spink instead went down in folklore - as both men recall that night to MATT BARLOW

description: Ben Wilde* was a popular and academic 14-year-old when he received a chatty Facebook message from a girl he'd never met, who claimed she was friends with someone on his school football team.
title: Ben was 14 when he was blackmailed online into sending explicit pictures. He tried to take his own life. But, unlike some other victims of 'sextortion', he survived to tell a story every parent should read

description: How can I say, out loud, that the day my son was born, and the brutal, postnatal, abstract hours since, have been the very worst days of my life?
title: Laura couldn't wait to be a mother. But within days of her son's birth she had descended into a hellish spiral of paranoia and delusions. Only when she woke up in a psychiatric ward did she discover the true cause...

description: A disturbing minute-by-minute journey detailing the array of chemicals, insidious synthetic materials and radioactive hazards we face from morning to night in our own homes.
title: From your alarm clock and mattress to your microwave and fridge - FRED KELLY reveals how your home could be slowly POISONING you

description: The 'true story' Netflix drama about a comedian targeted by a stalker has had 14 million viewers in the UK alone. Here we try to separate what is fact, what's embellished, and what is pure fiction...
title: 'People in the industry know who the "rapist" is': As Baby Reindeer is picked apart by online sleuths, we reveal exactly what is true, what's embellished... and what's pure fiction

description: Duane Eddy, the pioneering rock guitarist known for his instrumental 'twang', died on Tuesday at the age of 86. The musician gained fame with a string of hits in the late '50s and early '60s.
title: Duane Eddy, legendary 'twangy' guitarist famous for Peter Gunn theme and Rebel Rouser, dies at 86

description: Lottie Moss, 26, and former The Saturdays singer Una Healy, 41, are the latest celebs confirmed to appear in Bear Grylls' upcoming Netflix reality show Bear Hunt.
title: Lottie Moss and Una Healy 'sign up' for Holly Willoughby and Bear Grylls' upcoming Netflix reality show Bear Hunt as pair want fans to 'see a different side to them'

description: American pop music sensation SZA was on the verge of leaving one of her Australian concerts midway through the performance.
title: SZA calls out Australians over 'disgusting' act at her Melbourne show

description: Clarkson's Farm is set to return for a third series.
title: Clarkson's Farm Series 3: Jeremy Clarkson expresses heartbreak after revealing his beloved 'pet' cow Pepper has been taken to the abattoir

description: Jonathan Majors and his girlfriend Meagan Good couldn't keep their hands off each other during a sizzling trip to the beach in Malibu on Tuesday.
title: Jonathan Majors flashes ripped abs while kissing bikini-clad girlfriend Meagan Good on Malibu beach... after sentencing for domestic violence conviction

description: Researchers in London found smokers had 11 cigarettes per day on average in 2019. The figure stood at 14 in 2008. But the number hasn't shifted since.
title: Has WFH jeapordised UK's stop-smoking ambition? Decade-long decline in number of cigarettes smokers puff each day has stalled in wake of pandemic, study finds
